quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  83,1,Veylun lilmutaffifiyne
  83,2,Elleziyne izektalu ÂṀalennasi yestevfune
  83,3,Ve iza kaluhum ev vezenuhum yuhsirune
  83,4,Ela yezunnu ulaike ennehum mebÂṀusune
  83,5,Liyevmin ÂṀazÄḟymin
  83,6,Yevme yekumunnasu lirabbilÂṀalemiyne
  83,7,Kella inne kitabelfuccari lefiy sicciynin
  83,8,Ve ma edrake ma sicciynun
  83,9,Kitabun merkumun
  83,10,Veylun yevmeizin lilmukezzibiyne
  83,11,Elleziyne yukezzibune biyevmiddiyni
  83,12,Ve ma yukezzibu bihi illa kullu muÂṀtedin esiymin
  83,13,ÄḞza tutla aleyhi ayatuna kale esatÄḟyrulÂṀevveliyne
  83,14,Kella bel rane ÂṀala kulubihim ma kanu yeksibune
  83,15,Kella innehum ÂṀan rabbihim yevmeizin lemahcubune
  83,16,Summe innehum lesalulcahÄḟymi
  83,17,Summe yukalu hazelleziy kuntum bihi tukezzibune
  83,18,Kella inne kitabelÂṀebrari lefiy ÂṀÄḟlliyyiyne
  83,19,Ve ma edrake ma ÂṀÄḟlliyyune
  83,20,Kitabun merkumun
  83,21,YeÅheduhulmukarrebune
  83,22,ÄḞnnelebrare. Lefiy naÂṀÄḟymin
  83,23,ÂṀAlelÂṀeraiki yenzurune
  83,24,TaÂṀrifu fiy vucuhihim nadretennaÂṀÄḟymi
  83,25,Yuskavne min rahÄḟykÄḟn mahtumin
  83,26,HÄḟtamuhu miskun ve fiy zalike felyetenafesilmutenasifune
  83,27,Ve mizacuhu min tesniymin
  83,28,Aynen yeÅrebu bihelmukarrebune
  83,29,ÄḞnnelleziyne ecremu kanu minelleziyne amenu yadhakune
  83,30,Ve iza merru bihim yeteÄamezune
  83,31,Ve izenkalebu ila ehlihimunkalebu fekihiyne
  83,32,Ve iza reevhum kalu inne haulai ledallune
  83,33,Ve ma ursilu ÂṀaleyhim hafizÄḟyne
  83,34,Felyevmelleziyne amenu minelkuffari yadhakune
  83,35,ÂṀAlelÂṀeraiki yenzurune
  83,36,Hel suvvibelkuffaru ma kanu yefÂṀalune